everywhere with the aim of eventually removing the Holy Book from all scenes.
We all saw the <span class=SpellE>Quran</span> that <a
href="http://www.irna.com/occasion/ertehal/english/will/defs1.htm#ank18">Muhammad
Reza Khan <span class=SpellE>Pahlavi</span></a> <span class=GramE>...(</span>18)
had printed. He succeeded in deceiving some people including a few Muslim <span
