class=SpellE>Bani</span> <span class=SpellE>Omayyads</span></a> ...(47), who
were annihilated and cast into the Hell, reflect the cries of protest by the
people against the oppressors of the world and it is the perpetuation of such
cries of protest that shatters oppression. It is necessary that the crimes of
the tyrants in each age and era be regularly condemned in the cries of
lamentation and in the recitals of elegies held for the Infallible Imams. </span></p>

